42 header (ext) :					option + cmd + H

Copy selection :					cmd + C
Cut selection :						cmd + X
Paste :								cmd + V
Undo :								cmd + Z
Redo :								cmd + maj + Z

Go back :							ctrl + -
Go forward :						ctrl + maj + -

Comment a line :					cmd K + cmd C  or  cmd + /
Remove comment :					cmd K + cmd U  or  cmd + /

Move line up :						option + ↑
move line down :					option + ↓

Copy line up :						option + maj + ↑
Copy line down :					option + maj + ↓

Insert line up :					maj + cmd + enter
Insert line down :					enter (lol)

Join line with below one :			ctrl + j

Indent line right :					cmd + ]  or  Tab
Indent line left :					cmd + [  or  maj + Tab

Fold :								option + cmd + [  or  cmd K + cmd [
Unfold :							option + cmd + ]  or  cmd K + cmd ]
Unfold all :						cmd K  + cmd J

Select same word :					cmd + D
Invert characters with the next :	ctrl + T
Move selection to next match :		cmd K + cmd D
Rename symbol :						F2
Replace :							option + cmd + F

Delete all left :					cmd + backspace
Delete all right :					ctrl + K
Delete line :						maj + cmd + K

Go to definition :					F12
Open definition to the side :		cmd K + F12
Go to references :					maj + F12
Peek definition :					option + F12
Go to function :					cmd + T

Add Breakpoint :					F9